<emphasis bold="true" box="[1191,1207,747,773]" pageId="4" pageNumber="219">×</emphasis>
longer than wide (9: 3); 3 
<superScript attach="left" box="[219,233,782,796]" fontSize="6" pageId="4" pageNumber="219">rd</superScript>
antennomere 1.1 × 4 
<superScript attach="left" box="[472,485,782,796]" fontSize="6" pageId="4" pageNumber="219">th</superScript>
(11: 10); 3 
<superScript attach="left" box="[617,631,782,796]" fontSize="6" pageId="4" pageNumber="219">rd</superScript>
segment of maxillary palp of female 3.5 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1097,1113,783,809]" pageId="4" pageNumber="219">×</emphasis>
longer than maximally wide (14: 4); 5 
<superScript attach="left" box="[260,273,818,832]" fontSize="6" pageId="4" pageNumber="219">th</superScript>
segment 1.1 × length of 6 
<superScript attach="left" box="[560,573,818,832]" fontSize="6" pageId="4" pageNumber="219">th</superScript>
